{"tid":1638500,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屎忽痕： 新·18區 土地功能","createTime":"2019-10-08T10:33:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T12:18:34.000Z","uid":291987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6eec1e6fdbfeb6f46d91a1250ede176473afdda7","tid":1638500,"uid":291987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"［歡迎大家增添其他功能］<br />\n如果首都係沙田<br />\n咁聖城就一定係黃大仙！<br />\n<br />\n✺<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">首都：沙田</span></strong></span><br />\n民主運動初期，已完美展現和勇一家親，成各區榜樣。<br />\n上議院：連登（議政之用）<br />\n下議院：新城市廣場（集會、唱國歌、與商場保安、狗隻爭論執法議題之用）<br />\n地標：沙燕橋<br />\n盛產：沙田柚<br />\n<br />\n其他新社區功能包括：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">✺聖城：黃大仙</span></span></strong><br />\n居於聖城內嘅得道仙人不怕煙攻狗咬。<br />\n盛產：不鏽鋼碟（已開光）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>✺聖山：獅子山</strong></span></span><br />\n傳說聖山乃神獸［鶳］所棲身之聖域。聖山於日出掛直幡；於日入現聖光。<br />\n盛產：民主榮光<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>✺兵工廠：深水埗 </strong></span></span><br />\n國難五金、鴨寮街所在地。<br />\n盛產：防具、教學鐳射筆<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>✺新西軍營：荃灣</strong></span></span><br />\n新界一大戰綫，主要戰場：市中心<br />\n盛產：重型傷兵（sad but true...手足中刀又中槍）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>✺中心軍營：旺角、尖沙咀</strong></span></span><br />\n香港中心地段戰綫，主要戰場：狗屋<br />\n於新界九龍各區借兵，戰鬥經驗豐富，能力diverse，步兵系、遠程系、法師系⋯⋯<br />\n盛產：唔想過海嘅勇者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>✺新東軍營：坑口、寶林</strong></span></span><br />\n新東戰綫，主要戰場：黨鐵站。<br />\n盛產：被黨報文潰報質疑扮街坊嘅防守型勇者<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">✺心魔城：太古城</span></span></strong><br />\n城內住咗唔少好有地位嘅心靈魔法師。佢哋可以憑一句說話、一個屋企廁所就瞬間擊潰3萬隻狗嘅弱小心靈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盛產：稅收<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">✺連儂牧場：屯門</span></strong></span><br />\n牛牛養殖場。獨特飼養方法係每日聽《願榮光歸香港》培養抗爭和正面情緒。<br />\n並非以肉質分類，屯門牛牛以決心分為鬥牛、武牛同埋和牛。<br />\n盛產：牛牛<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">✺Art Gallery：大埔連儂隧道</span></span></strong><br />\n民間藝術家以圖切磋技藝。名作包括：超大型香蕉糖人像畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、4D動感文宣（包括：拖鞋敲擊、噴水等）<br />\n盛產：創意<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>✺新&middot;紅館：香港太空館外空地</strong></span></span><br />\n回水激光show不定期上演。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">✺英靈碑：金鐘PP</span></strong></span><br />\n🎗<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">✺力場防護罩：深水灣79號</span></span></strong><br />\n香港人最強大台<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">✺Camino Finisterre：朝聖之路，路線係由各位家中出發至煲底。</span></strong></span><br />\n期望同各位手足有日除下面罩，<br />\n於煲底相見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邪魔之地：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>&Psi;百畝森林：灣仔至西環一帶</strong></span></span><br />\nYellow Object習維尼啲𡃁嘅聚居地，當中包括中聯辦、老解、㭍婆、賣港行會卅二魔、大公報、禮義廉等。<br />\n盛產：魑魅魍魎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">&Psi;阿布之鄉：元朗六鄉</span></strong></span><br />\n充斥住一班香港阿布，以原居民所享獲嘅傳統權益胡作非為。為擺脫「牛屎佬」嘅矮化形象，7&middot;21六鄉集結，用藤條將「官&middot;警&middot;黑」打拼出新中文字！傳聞班阿布正向聯合國申請將新字列入文化遺產。<br />\n盛產：六鄉各有不同特産，如：錦田沙埔村賣嘅人血西瓜/ 八鄉好hit嘅光頭look（強光能反射各種道德審查，強大無恥心靈）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">&Psi;門虫角：北角</span></strong></span><br />\n爬行種&mdash;&mdash;門虫，屬低等物種，經幾代產卵繁殖後衍生成幫。手能變形成竹枝/刀，成為「手臂嘅延伸」。8&middot;11疑炎夏引起虫患肆虐，一幫門虫於街上無差別攻擊人類。<br />\n盛產：門虫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">&Psi;香港百慕達：太子黨鐵站</span></strong></span><br />\n香港百慕達今年8月出現史前生物速龍！8&middot;31列車駛入此站後，乘客無辜地被失控嘅「狂暴速龍」攻擊同咬傷！另外，响設施運作順暢嘅情況下，無理關站2日。7分鐘時空畫面離奇消失！ ！3位手足下落不明！！！<br />\n盛產：奇案、冤案、白花<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">&Psi;霞姨片場：觀塘黨鐵站</span></strong></span><br />\n聽聞劇目「站體自燃」穿崩片段流出後，有幾個臨時演員被霞姨拖數同冇得拎飯盒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盛產：臨時演員<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">&Psi;工賊城寨：土瓜灣</span></strong></span><br />\n香城暴徒始祖藏身之處，令城寨內污煙瘴氣。暴徒始祖擅長製作炸彈、汽油彈及發動暴動。<br />\n盛產：土製菠蘿<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">&Psi; 集中營：新屋嶺</span></strong></span><br />\n說不出聲的淪陷區<br />\n盛產：酷刑"},{"pid":"5531bc9394927cc8b638e8c490b4ddf479e59b6b","tid":1638500,"uid":50848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:35:59.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985baf14bd3f1b8d274413a7b0007fc1a11d1cf7","tid":1638500,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:42:32.000Z","msg":"True but sad <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望我地的後代會永記我們這段歷史"},{"pid":"bf413c41f83e54305e88dbbfb47e4e3b7077cb5f","tid":1638500,"uid":291987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"985baf14bd3f1b8d274413a7b0007fc1a11d1cf7","tid":1638500,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:42:32.000Z","msg":"True but sad <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望我地的後代會永記我們這段歷史"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}